<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c1">" ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"الدراية"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٢٧٨)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
